&lt;p&gt;Our Paediatric Decision Unit (PDU) is dedicated to the care of children up to the age of 16 years attending the Emergency Department. In addition to a separate children’s waiting room and a triage room we have 11 beds for observation and treatment.&lt;br /&gt;&lt;br /&gt;This post offers the opportunity to develop your clinical, A&amp;E and leadership skills in a friendly, fast paced, dynamic environment.&lt;br /&gt;&lt;br /&gt;You are ideally a Registered Children’s Nurse with a professional approach to delivering high quality, patient focused care. Our Children’s Practice Development Nurse works as part of the nursing team to provide support for your orientation and ongoing professional development.&lt;br /&gt;&lt;br /&gt;Please note that short-listed candidates are able to arrange an informal visit prior to interview on request.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;For further details / informal visits contact:&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Jo leverton&lt;/p&gt;
